
= Cluster-Governed Forecasting for Financial Planning under Uncertainty
*Leonardo Bornhäußer · Tuna (R&D Lead) · Creativate Research Group*

== Abstract
We present a clustered-forecasting architecture derived from the Neural Enterprise Network (NEN) for financial OPEX planning.
By linking Finance, HR, and Operations clusters, we improve accuracy and calibrated uncertainty.

